SELL
  Offer commodities for sale on the open market.

SYNTAX
  sell <commodity> <x,y> <amount> <price>

DESCRIPTION
  Places a commodity lot for sale on the market.  Other players
  can buy it with the 'buy' command.  The lot remains available
  for several updates.

  <commodity>  - single letter: f=food i=iron l=lcm d=dust etc.
  <x,y>        - sector where the goods currently are
  <amount>     - how many units to sell
  <price>      - price per unit in dollars

  Goods are held in escrow at the source sector until sold or the
  lot expires.  If unsold, goods return to the sector.

  Use 'trade' to see what is currently on the market.

EXAMPLE
  sell food 0,0 500 3.50    sell 500 food at $3.50/unit
  sell iron 0,0 200 8.00    sell 200 iron at $8/unit

